data.description: Come see this spacious 3-bedroom stone home in a desirable Brown Deer area is a perfect find for both homeowners and investors. With 3 full bathrooms. Home offers vaulted ceilings, natural stone fireplace off the dining room and kitchen. This home sits off a large corner lot, with a large circular driveway. Nice fenced in backyard, home offers tons of  potential for customization. Priced below its assessed value. Please read private remarks before scheduling!
